  "title": "Enchantment Reveal",
  "description": "A mod that let's you see all of the enchantments you'll get in the enchantment table",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⚠️ Not for servers!!!</strong></h1>\n\n<h2><strong>About</strong></h2>\n<p>Say farewell to random outcomes and hello to a world where your gear is tailored to perfection.<br><br>\nEnchantment Reveal lets you preview all potential enchantments, allowing you to see exactly what you are going to get without relying on luck or guesswork.<br><br></p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>The mod only works in singleplayer and <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">NOT IN SERVERS</span>. due to the way vanilla's player data saving works on servers.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2><strong>View in enchantment table</strong></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/946157/description_215274ec-0d1f-468b-ac6b-e8a83941fa5b.png\" alt=\"Preview\" width=\"828\" height=\"664\"></p>\n\n<h2><strong>Supported Versions</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/185/822/256/256/636829723898798601.png\" alt=\"Fabric API - Minecraft Mods - CurseForge\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\">\n    Fabric 1.19.2 - 1.20.4 (<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Requires Fabric API</a>)\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1003537/description_fddab02e-963a-4335-8cb2-48ac035fecb5.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\">\n    Forge 1.19.2 - 1.20.4\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<table style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/CrownSheep/Enchantment-Reveal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/25/25231.png\" alt=\"GitHub Logo\" width=\"80\"><br>\n        <strong>‎ ‎ ‎ GitHub</strong>\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/enchantment-reveal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        ‎ ‎ ‎<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81b12a5bce3d683ff55d209e677fec6677090d24.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Logo\" width=\"70\"><br>\n        <strong>CurseForge</strong>\n      </a>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>",
